'''University of Creative Technology, Chittagong''' ('''UCTC''') is a private university in [[Chittagong]], [[Bangladesh]]. It was established in 2015 under the Private University Act, 2010.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sai.uni-heidelberg.de/workgroups/bdlaw/1992-a34.htm |title=The Private University Act, 1992 |website=The Heidelberg Bangladesh Law Translation Project |publisher=Heidelberg University |accessdate=June 25, 2007}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Bangladesh government approves six more private universities |url=http://bdnews24.com/education/2016/01/10/bangladesh-government-approves-six-more-private-universities |newspaper=bdnews24.com |access-date=2016-06-28}}</ref> The university offers undergraduate and post-graduate programmes taught in English.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theindependentbd.com/home/printnews/77172|title=Only 12 out of 51 move to permanent campuses {{!}} Independent|website=www.theindependentbd.com|access-date=2018-06-10}}</ref>
